title: Dexter.S03E07_720p_to_1056x594_AC3_for_XBMC.avi
description:
This is a conversion from the DIMENSION x264 720p AC3 original to an XBMC compatible version at 1056x594, which is the maximum resolution playable on the XBox hardware for a 16:9 aspect ratio video.

Video:  XVid (1056x594 16:9), 3998 Kbps, 23.976 fps 
Audio:  AC3 6ch 384 Kbps
Length: 56:57 min

Enjoy and I welcome any feedback about playability on the Xbox with XBMC.	

Some XBMC configuration notes:
- Make sure you have the latest build of XBMC
- Disable all unneeded tasks like FTP or HTTP server, RSS Feed display
- Turn off Flicker Filter and Soften for Video settings
